  <div class="stack">
    <main class="container about">
      <section class="flow">
        <h2 id="who-am-i-">Who am I?</h2>
        <p>
          <em>Just a little bit about me:</em> My education background is in technology from <a href="https://polytechnic.purdue.edu/departments/computer-graphics-technology" target="_blank">Purdue University</a>.
          I have grown in my career from being a visual designer -> UI developer
